    "description": "Patatas a lo pobre is a traditional dish from Andalusia and in this rendition, you'll bake potatoes, green pepper and onion until soft and charred. Pair this with crispy haddock bites, a fresh tomato salsa and some aioli for a full Spanish takeout experience!",
